statements: SELECT lead_id, lead_name, interaction_date, interaction_type, preference_1, preference_2 FROM lead_engagement;
SELECT lead_name, interaction_type, preference_1 FROM lead_engagement WHERE lead_id = 101;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, interaction_date FROM lead_engagement WHERE interaction_type = 'Email' ORDER BY interaction_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_engagement WHERE preference_1 = 'Tech' AND preference_2 = 'Gaming';
SELECT lead_id, lead_name, interaction_date, interaction_type FROM lead_engagement WHERE interaction_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY interaction_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM lead_engagement WHERE interaction_type = 'Meeting' ORDER BY interaction_date DESC;
SELECT lead_name, interaction_type, interaction_date FROM lead_engagement WHERE interaction_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT DISTINCT preference_1, preference_2 FROM lead_engagement WHERE preference_1 IS NOT NULL AND preference_2 IS NOT NULL;
SELECT lead_name, interaction_type, COUNT(*) AS interaction_count FROM lead_engagement GROUP BY lead_name, interaction_type;
SELECT lead_name, interaction_date, preference_1, preference_2 FROM lead_engagement WHERE interaction_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-01' ORDER BY preference_1 ASC, preference_2 DESC;
SELECT * FROM engagements;
